              <section class="mb-6">
                <h2
                  class="mb-2 text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white"
                >
                  @Investor Agent
                </h2>
                <p class="mb-4">
                  This AI Agent emulates the strategy and techniques how to
                  evaluate each stock based on the personality of the Investor.
                  Currently we support:
                </p>

                <ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-3 space-y-1">
                  <li>Warren Buffet</li>
                  <li>Charlie Munger</li>
                  <li>Bill Ackman</li>
                  <li>Michael Burry</li>
                  <li>Peter Lynch</li>
                  <li>Benjamin Graham</li>
                  <li>Cathie Wood</li>
                </ul>

                <div class="mb-2">
                  <strong>Prerequisite:</strong>
                  You must pick a personality and provide at least one stock ticker
                  (e.g. AMD).
                </div>

